com.hazelcast.jclouds

Class ComputeServiceBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.jclouds.ComputeServiceBuilder

  • public class ComputeServiceBuilder
extends Object
    ComputeServiceBuilder is the responsible class for building jclouds compute service provider. Also parses config and applies necessary filters on cluster nodes.
